<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <% include ../../partials/head %>
</head>
<body class="fixed-nav sticky-footer bg-dark" id="page-top">
  <!-- Navigation-->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top" id="mainNav">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="index.html">Bot Portal Config Setup</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="content-wrapper small-margin">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h1>Dimension Data Bot Portal - First time setup</h1>
          <p>Please initalise the bot portal, by adding the LUIS Region and <a target="_blank" href="https://portal.azure.com/#blade/HubsExtension/BrowseResourceBlade/resourceType/Microsoft.CognitiveServices%2Faccounts">Ocp Apim Subscription Key - If you do not see a coginative service, add a Luis Learning</a>
          </p>
          <p>In order for the portal to work effectively, please add the main department responsible for managing the Azure Subscription (This will be the main department for the super user) - <span class="text-warning">This will be assigned to your account</span></p>
          <form action="/install" method="post">
            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-group col-md-4">
                <label for="departmentName">Department Name</label>
                <input required type="text" class="form-control" id="departmentName" name="name" placeholder="Please enter Main deparment name...">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-5">
                <label for="Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key">Ocp Apim Subscription Key</label>
                <input required type="text" class="form-control" id="Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key" name="subKey" placeholder="Please enter Subscription Key">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="luisRegion">LUIS Region</label>
                <select required id="luisRegion" name="luisRegion" class="form-control">
                  <option>westus</option>
                  <option>westeurope</option>
                  <option>australiaeast</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Continue</button> 
          </form>        
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.container-fluid-->
   
<% include ../../partials/footer %>


</body>
</html>
